<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><strong>战术小组组长Nakamura的人事档案</strong></span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/local--files/30001/security.jpg" height="170dx" width="300dx" alt="security.jpg" class="image" /><br />
