</div>
<hr />
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/nakamura-s-personnel-file/nakamura.png" style="width:300px;" width="200dx" alt="nakamura.png" class="image" />
